author: Audrey McNamara
title: Protesters demonstrate against stay-at-home order at Michigan Capitol
description: Protesters in cars honked their horns and decorated their vehicles with flags in support of President Trump, and signs reading "let us work."
content: Michigan residents who oppose Governor Gretchen Whitmer's stay-at-home order blocked traffic Wednesday by descending on the state's Capitol in Lansing. Protesters in cars honked their horns and decorated their vehicles with flags in support of President Trump… [+1868 chars]
